Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The distance between two people's love and hate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two people's deduction and suspense
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.47,0:00:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A surprise trick in a questionable apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:09.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees through the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No case is left unsolved with Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.14,0:01:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We met a grandpa at Araide Clinic and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,heard a bizarre ghost story from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we came to his small old apartment house which
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he said was haunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, there is a building next to his apartment house
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The builder had committed suicide after the bursting of the financial bubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is a park in front of his apartment house too,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where the burned body of a young woman was previously found.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place has many eerie stories surrounding it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and we fell asleep while waiting in grandfather's room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:18.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for the ghost to appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out of here... Get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:33.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The toilet water turned red
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A spooky figure looks in through the window from outside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A sped \« figure looks in through the window from outside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a supernatural fiery ball
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:49.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,IS said to appear in the building next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does this mean anyhow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghost appearing on the TV screen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after suddenly fainting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The toilet water suddenly turning red.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:07.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both can be explained scientifically
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but what about the other two phenomenon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the death candle and the figure in the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just can't seem to figure them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did the culprit do them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there a culprit in the! first places
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If one did exist
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:27.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And for what purpose\NIS the culprit doing all this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Truth of the Haunted House (Part II)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you looking at with the window open?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bugs will come flying in again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm wondering just about where that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,gramps saw the death candle in that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The spot where I saw it is in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,around the center of that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The red light alone was looming and moving about in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At times it turned a bluish white light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:16.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't believe me, go ask\NHouichi Otonashi\NI ll') u\N6 META
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yotsuya of Room #2 and\NMr. Bancho of Room #4.\NHouichi Otonashi\N5 WMMmMEA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:22.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each of them said that they once also saw the death candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. yeah, I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A red one and blue death candle as w\NIwahisa Yotsuya\NNe B22)\N2 LoASM¢N AN\NQQIEA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I visited the room where my senior at school was livin\NIwahisa Yotsuya ma AM (22)\NCILIA\NSCHEME A
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your senior?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the room right above this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Room #6 is where my senior was living.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since then, he was unable to sleep properly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he was seized with fear of the death candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He finally moved out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was unable to sleep either, not because of fright,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but rather. because of being overexcited.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. this is a 8mm movie projector. right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm now using it to edit a movie filmed by our film club in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this room is bloody awful, full of sick horror magazines and posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel I'm going to have nightmares just being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still. all this is nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,compared to\NRoom #4 where Mr.Bancho lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this room is really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There're tons of the ghost and monster figures here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kikuji Banhou\N&% BY 3% Xx (34)\N4§I&A
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't seen anything yet.\NKikuji Banhou\NFE BI BT Xx (34)\NCS LQUOQL.\NAB EEA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kikuji Banhou\NFE BY 5 Xx (34) aiiéA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I turn the light off like so\NKikuji Banhou\NZE BY [ ox (34)\NAMET A
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I turn the light off like so
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:36.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yipes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1. The figures... are glowing various colors in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because of this black light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The special kind of fluorescent coating painted on the figures
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,reacts to black light making them glow like a neon tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm... You know a lot, sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A toy store owner told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, you also saw the death candle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but'l saw it through that window
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,not the window facing that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This window is located diagonally
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,below the window where the figure appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think you better close the window now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do it for our sister's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, in fact, a couple of moths have already entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't believe the ghost story I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you better go talk with Botan of Room #1.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That-square grad student with a square head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:33.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe nothing but what I can comprehend scientifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsuyuhiko Botan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsuyuhiko Botan\NHR RE QR)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know what I hate more than that now?\NTsuyuhiko Botan\NHF mE (27)\N<LI.\NTS EREA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsuyuhiko Botan\NHA BE (27) kL} {IN
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That building opposite here that is still half done.\NTsuyuhiko Botan\NHER REED
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That building opposite here that is still half done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, sO. get a load of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That goddamn building shuts out the sunlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so the sun rarely shines into the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's certainly true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr.Otonashi's room diagonally above is much better than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it has a window facing the street side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:08.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So. why don't you move out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the rent is so cheap and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:12.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,my grandma told me that this place had good feng shun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you say you believe only what you can comprehend scientifically, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. May I.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Smoke here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But please leave after you finish smoking the cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah".<... Ahh
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D... Dad... your arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A moth again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darn! Why always me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get them out of the room quickly! Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm trying to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprits were afraid that the murder they committed would be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they tried to destroy the decisive evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:09.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of the woman that they burned to death 4 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:12.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They used ghosts to cover up the evildoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?Are you leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The night's still young
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:22.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may be missing out on seeing one of the eeriest ghosts
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you've ever seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad you're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it'spperfectly all right with me\NIf you leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way I can get on with my paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,buddy, take it easy. say hello to the ghost for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heigh-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How unsociable they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Faugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haunted by the ghost. my eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making such a big fuss over illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm.? Where is Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:47.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. there he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! We're going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got to go pee. but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit scared to go alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. pops. please go with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:00.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, why should I?\NAll right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting outside then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I've seen him somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:20.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sonny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ook. That restroom is cursed\NNo doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so stinky and I can't flush the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it sure smells. but
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There seems no problem with flushing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wa-water is... Water is turning red
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tha-that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. boy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, the TV in your room is cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look. over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghost! That's the ghost!\NWhat should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?\NThere is no tape inside
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,WwW. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! So it appeared again! The ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There must be something wrong here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because everything was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.06,0:10:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were all tricks to make it look like the works of the ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying that nobody but you could have set the tricks up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because you created them. isn't that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bancho?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tricks.\NHow can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man. you're acting like a detective or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De-detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you are the renowned detective
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I'm gonna unlock
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the mysteries of a lot of psychic phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:37.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First of all, about the toilet water turning red.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I noticed about it was that, when I entered the restroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it smelled awfully of ammonia, and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that the toilet tank smelled faintly of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ammonia and alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you did an experiment in
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:56.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,science in your elementary school days, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you add one drop of alkaline ammonia water to the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:05.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,colorless phenolphthalein solution dissolved in alcohol,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the red color will appear like magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but,\NI wonder if it would work out that well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The color in the experiment isn't bright red but pinkish red.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The color could never be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it would look like blood in a dimly-lit restroom like here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well. even so
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there is no chemical reaction with urine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because ammonia in our urine Is acid or neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not alkaline.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. that's why he needed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,this ammonia liquid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1S IS pourec IN 0 e wa er in the toilet bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then phenolphthalein is poured into the water in the toilet tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:53.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then chemical reaction will occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And nobody would suspect the strong smell of ammonia
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,seeing this dirty restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But.\NWhere did you get that chemical, sonny?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pops asked me to look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when you were saying goodbye at the entrance,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.63,0:13:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I slipped into the room and found it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in this room. Mr. Bancho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also found other interesting things
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iike phenolphthalein and chloroform.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:23.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even a video tape of a Cary movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A scary movie video tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! The tape with a ghost woman
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,saying. Go home, go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He-hey
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D.Don't tell me that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,CC <oo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real identity of the ghost my daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran saw on the TV screen are the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,pictures Mr. Bancho transmitted from the VCR in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He-he sent the pictures! How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's simple and easy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you use the public antenna of this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plug the antenna cord into the output terminal of the VCR in his room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and transmit video pictures to the antenna
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the antenna sends the pictures
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to the TV in Mr. Otonashfs room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:19.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to do that, you have to be able to set the TV channel
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to the appropriate channel to receive the pictures
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you must turn on the TV first, how do you think
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:27.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a multi channel remote control
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr Otonashi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once you enter the name of the manufacturer of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your TV or VCR into the device
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can operate any TV or VCR made by the manufacturer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So with the multi channel remote control,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:38.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can operate the TV in someone else's room on
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:39.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,without the owner realizing a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:42.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after finding out how the trick worked
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it was a piece of cake even for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This old man was the one who sent the images to my TV screen a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got him to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,send the video I just borrowed from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used the remote control
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from outside the window of Mr. Othonashi's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Facing the building under construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:07.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using the wall as a foothold,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you could easily send the signals to his TV set from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't even need to watch the TV screen since
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the video was played repeatedly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you had to do was listen to the sound from the TV and set the channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And while the sun was still up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You poured the chloroform onto the windowsill
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so that all of us who were in the room would fall asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You thought you could make
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,one of us who suddenly fainted and got up in the dark room, still
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hazy in the head see an eerie illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:43.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But, that was for real. wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:50.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean the figure of a person that has been looking this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. that's not a figure of a person at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go over and look closer, you'll see what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This... this is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moths gathered in large numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or, to put it more precisely
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's an aggregate of male moths.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:16.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He coated the screen in a human shape with female moth pheromone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that is also used as an insecticide, and stuck eyes and a mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,made from black paper on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The male moths that were attracted to the scent of the pheromone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,clustered on it to make it\NIook like a human shadow was
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iooking inside through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, moths kept approaching my arm several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I almost fell from the window where I saw the figure for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found myself grabbing the screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and got the pheromone on my arm, which attracted moths to me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So. that is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I simply removed the screen on the second floor and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,placed it by window on the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incidentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:17:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason why the figure started on its own is disappearing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because Mr. Bansho's black light that was activated by a timer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was emitted from the window of his room diagonally below.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moths are more prone to be attracted by
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:17.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ultraviolet light emitted by the black lights, than the pheromone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the trick would be disclosed if even one moth remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Mr. Bancho hurried across to the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as soon as the moths began to fly out. then
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,opened the window and screen together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The force of the impact knocked the moths off the screen completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bancho, you pretended not to notice the moths even
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when you got close to the window. right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because you intentionally caused this uproar over the ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But. I still don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the chemicals besides the chloroform can be gotten easily. but why
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:17:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bancho could've easily made the video himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by using his scary figures and his falsetto
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd he go through the trouble of making up a ghost story?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:13.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He attempted to scare us,\NMr. Otonashi's guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To get Mr. Otonashi who refused to move to decide to do after all this ghost scare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps. in order to cover up the crime four years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crime four years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the murder of the the woman burned to death in the park?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You say you saw the death candle in that building under construction?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was drifting in the air wasn't the death candle, but a lit cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was glowing bluish white
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was the light of portable TV that was secretly being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!? Don't tell me there's someone in that building?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:19:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, taking advantage of the fact the building is still under construction,
